column5: Thanks for the input. I can't find Gull Rock on my map. Could you provide me with a little more direction.Thanks

It is in the same chain of lakes. On the way from Ear Falls to Red Lake, it is on the east side of the road, where pakwash is on the left. Gull Rock is closer to Red Lake. It is very similar to Pakwash in lake type, but I think it has a better concentration of fish. Let me know if I can be of anymore help to you.
